# Manage with a Server SDK {% #server-sdks %}

You can also manage project variables programmatically using a [Server SDK](/docs/sdks#server). Each call requires an [API key](/docs/advanced/security/api-keys) with the `project.write` scope to create, update, or delete variables, or the `project.read` scope to list and read them.

## Create a variable {% #create-variable %}

