{% tabsitem #react-native title="React Native" %}
If using Expo, set the URL scheme to `appwrite-callback-<PROJECT_ID>` in your `app.json` file.

```json
{
  "expo": {
    "scheme": "appwrite-callback-<PROJECT_ID>"
  }
