{% tabsitem #server-sdk title="Server SDK" %}
You can also create tables programmatically using a [Server SDK](/docs/sdks#server). Appwrite [Server SDKs](/docs/sdks#server) require an [API key](/docs/advanced/security/api-keys).

{% multicode %}

```server-nodejs
const sdk = require('node-appwrite');

// Init SDK
const client = new sdk.Client();

